Title: Herrera - HRA-06 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Make your space stand out with an eye-catching time-worn aesthetic when you install this wool HRA-06 area rug from Kaleen's Herrera collection..

  • The Herrera collection from Kaleen features hand-knotted area rugs made from wool with a neutral color palette and traditional designs.
  • Wool is an absorbent material, and your rug will last longer if you keep it in a zone that's protected from excess moisture.
  • Wool rugs shed when they're new because of the weaving process, and you can control it by vacuuming without a beater bar a few times per week.
  • Follow the care tag instructions when cleaning messes or spills to reduce the risk of staining.

Add old-world charm to your home when you roll out this beautiful 3207 wool area rug from the Helena collection from Kaleen.

Title: Herrera - HRA-07 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Bring an elegant vintage look into any room with this handmade wool HRA-07 area rug from Kaleen's Herrera collection..

  • The Herrera collection from Kaleen features hand-knotted area rugs made from quality wool with a neutral palette and range of traditional designs.
  • Because wool is absorbent, we recommend placing wool rugs in low-traffic zones that are protected from high levels of shoe traffic and moisture.
  • If you notice shedding when your wool rug is new, use a vacuum with the beater bar turned off to control it.
  • Use a wool detergent and follow the care tag instructions to minimize the risk of staining from messes or spills.

Title: Brooklyn - 5309 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Masterfully hand-tufted of wool by talented artisans, the Kaleen Brooklyn 5309 rug promises a rich, long-lasting texture. Plus, this piece features handsome floral motifs for timeless style that can go anywhere-casual or formal spaces..

  • A natural insulator, the Brooklyn collection is hand-tufted of super soft wool for exceptional comfort underfoot.
  • From its earthy hues to the traditional floral motifs, this classic rug adds a refined look to any living or dining area.
  • Our hand-tufted wool rugs feature a medium pile height for remarkable comfort.
  • Maintain a clean, healthy rug by vacuuming regularly and cleaning with a soft brush when necessary.

Title: Zuma Beach - ZUM-10 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
With the Zuma Beach collection by Kaleen, you can bring a touch of bohemian flair to any of your favorite spaces indoors and outdoors alike. The gorgeous ZUM-10 area rug enjoys a creative vintage look - its intricate regional patterns awash with a lightly distressed color treatment.

  • This strong synthetic area rug is built to stand up to even the most demanding placements. ZUM-10 is resistant to moisture, fading, and the wear of frequent foot traffic.
  • Bold borders make this bohemian area rug an especially effective way to frame a functional arrangement like a dining table or a patio seating area.
  • Each synthetic area rug in the Zuma Beach collection is machine-made from 100% polypropylene worked into a low and practical pile for easy maintenance.
  • Vacuum using a suction-only setting. Treat difficult soil with gentle soap and water, then rinse thoroughly.

Title: Brooklyn - 5307 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Our Kaleen Brooklyn 5307 area rug is beloved for how it looks and feels. Featuring a captivating bohemian design and natural, hand-tufted wool construction, it's a true sensory treat that's sure to last a long time..

  • The Brooklyn collection boasts an extremely soft surface due to its hand-tufted construction of 100% wool fibers.
  • For instant visual interest, add this chic, bohemian floor covering to your entryway, master suite, or hallway.
  • A medium pile of hand-tufted wool grants our stylish indoor rug outstanding comfort underfoot.
  • To keep this rug in peak shape, regularly vacuum and cleaning with a soft brush on occasion.

Title: Zuma Beach - ZUM-01 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Do you want to bring more boho decor into your home? Do it with this ZUM-01 area rug from the Zuma Beach collection.

  • The Zuma Beach collection features bohemian-inspired designs, synthetic durability, and affordable prices.
  • This stunning rug comes in two colors-choose between them based on which one will fit your space's color palette.
  • We recommend pairing this rug with a quality rug pad to prevent sliding and friction damage to the 1/4" synthetic pile and backing.
  • Rotate your rug and pad annually and turn off the beater bar when vacuuming to keep the pile in good condition.

Body (HTML):
Our Kaleen Alejandra ALJ99 rug is hand-woven of natural jute and wool by skilled artisans and embellished with elephant-style tassels for incredible texture and depth. Even better, this piece is easy to care for.

  • A true work of art, this collection is meticulously hand-woven by artisans of jute and wool, giving it exceptional comfort underfoot.
  • Southwestern motifs give this floor covering a distinct look that adds a captivating focal point to your living room, bedroom, or office.
  • Featuring a plush pile of hand-woven jute and wool yarns, this indoor area rug is both soft and resilient.
  • Protect your rug from everyday wear by vacuuming it regularly on top and below.
  • Made in India.

Title: Rila - ILA-01 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Rich classic styling can fit anywhere in your home with the versatile Rila collection by Kaleen. The gorgeous ILA-01 area rug draws from an endless well of historical inspiration, presenting an elegant medallion design flanked by layered borders and intricate detailing throughout.

  • Each rug in the Rila collection is constructed with an open-backed design - lightweight and easy to rearrange as the whim strikes you.
  • Rich saffron orange, merlot red, and light golds give this traditional area rug a warm and inviting appearance, brightened with a splash of sky blue for contrast.
  • ILA-01 is a machine-made 100% polyester area rug. Each end is capped in a short-cropped fringe.
  • Vacuum using suction only. Quickly blot away spills with a dry white cloth before they set.

Title: Shades - SHD-01 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Instant drama awaits with the bold SHD-01 area rug, its ombre coloration sure to transform any environment it occupies. This piece is part of the Shades collection from Kaleen, a series of practical wool rugs that make an unforgettable statement through innovative color compositions.

  • This rug is made strong for excellent performance in all your most active interior placements. These rugs are soft enough for quiet spaces like bedrooms and durable enough for living rooms shared with pets, children, and heavy foot traffic.
  • Choose from a diverse variety of vibrant colorways. Each contemporary rug in the Shades collection features a striped design that goes from dark to light and back again to create a striking ombre pattern. Space-dyed coloration lends added tonality to the palette.
  • Each rug in the Shades collection is hand-loomed by skilled Kaleen weavers for artisanal appeal in every detail. The plush 100% wool rug pile features a cut texture for velvety softness. Sturdy cotton canvas lends added stability to the backing.
  • Use a dry white cloth to blot spills immediately upon noticing. When vacuuming, use a suction-only setting or hard surface attachment.

Title: Imprints Modern - IPM-02 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Are you looking for quality contemporary decor? Capture the look that you want with this IPM-02 area rug from Kaleen's Imprints Modern collection..

  • The Imprints Modern collection from Kaleen features contemporary area rugs with beautiful colors and handmade virgin wool pile.
  • Consider which color variant of this rug fits in with the color palette of the space that you're decorating to find a good match.
  • All wool rugs are prone to shedding, and it is more common when they're new-keep the 3/8" wool pile while controlling shedding by vacuuming with no beater bar.
  • Use a wool specific soap to protect the fibers in addition to following the manufacturer's cleaning instructions.

Title: Sunice - SUN-06 Area Rug

Timeless sophistication gets a modern twist with the vibrant tones and indoor-outdoor versatility of our Kaleen Sunice SUN-06 rug. Crafted of synthetic yarns, this long-lasting piece is stylish and strong..

  • The Zuma Beach collection features synthetic area rugs that are affordable, durable, and perfect for today's trends.

Title: Brushstrokes - BRS-04 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Enjoy an artful treat for the senses with the Brushstrokes BRS-04 area rug by Kaleen. This laidback design captures attention with its tie-dye visual effect, made from soft natural wool in creative nature-inspired hues..

  • Brushstrokes collection area rugs employ a unique primitive dyeing method to infuse each yarn with a rich and dimensional color profile.
  • Use this contemporary rug to soften a casual seating space, to bring a pop of color to the home office, or to underscore your bohemian bedroom decor.
  • Skilled artisans tuft each wool rug yarn by hand. The pile is kept low and manageable, backed with cotton canvas for extra stability and support.
  • Professional cleaning is recommended. Use a dry white cloth to gently blot away spills as soon as you encounter them.

Title: Marble - MBL-07 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
You'll do a doubletake every time you walk into the room with this MBL-07 area rug from Kaleen's Marble collection..

  • The Marble collection from Kaleen features stunning wool area rugs with marbled designs and natural colors.
  • Wool is an absorbent fiber that's sensitive to moisture and soil, so place your new rug in a dry room that's protected from heavy traffic.
  • We recommend a quality rug pad to prevent sliding on hard floors, keeping the backing and 3/8" wool pile in good condition.
  • To control wool shedding, vacuum a few times a week with the beater bar turned off to avoid causing wear to the yarn.

Title: Brushstrokes - BRS-06 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Energize your favorite space with the Brushstrokes BRS-06 area rug by Kaleen. This exciting design features dynamic interactions between color and form, an artistic impression captured in 100% wool pile for comfortable everyday appeal..

  • Kaleen employs a primitive dyeing method to achieve the rich tonal variation found within each yarn.
  • Color blooms across the surface, unbound by border. This contemporary area rug is available in a curated selection of colorways - bold, subdued, and in between.
  • Each yarn in the low-cut 100% wool rug pile is hand-tufted by skilled Kaleen artisans. A cotton backing provides added structural stability for lasting strength.
  • Vacuum using suction only - avoid using any type of brush roll or beater bar component. Invest in professional cleaning periodically.

Title: Zuma Beach - ZUM-08 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Add a dash of artistic expression to your favorite space with the Zuma Beach ZUM-08 area rug by Kaleen. This delightful design goes bold energetic colors over a versatile neutral field, abrash striations spanning the surface for a clever vintage look.

  • Zuma Beach collection area rugs are made from strong synthetic fibers for use indoors and outdoors alike - resistant to fading, staining, moisture, and wear.
  • Use this transitional area rug to brighten a balcony, to soften your step on the patio, or take advantage of its durable appeal to decorate hardwearing interior placements like a dining room or entryway.
  • ZUM-08 is a 100% polypropylene area rug machine-made with a dense low-woven pile, easy to clean and maintain for a fresh look that lasts.
  • Use gentle soap to spot clean soiled areas as needed. Rinse thoroughly.

Title: Textura - TXT-04 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Combining understated sophistication and a timeless, ogee motif-inspired design, our Kaleen Textura TXT-04 rug effortlessly blends with a wide range of styles, especially because it's hand-tufted of pure wool..

  • Super soft and inherently resilient, the Textura collection is hand-tufted of 100% wool by master artisans.
  • Past and present work in perfect harmony with this transitional piece's classic-yet-contemporary design that breathes life into any living, dining, or entertaining space.
  • Wool fibers make our hand-tufted indoor rug and its medium pile height incredibly soft.
  • Simply vacuum on top and beneath for regular cleaning of this area rug.

Title: Marble - MBL-03 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Bring natural patterns and textures into your space with this MBL-03 area rug from Kaleen's Marble collection..

  • The Marble collection from Kaleen features handmade wool area rugs with beautiful stone-inspired designs that'll be an instant conversation starter in your home.
  • Wool is sensitive to moisture and lasts longer when protected from heavy traffic, so choose a dry room with minimal shoe traffic for best results.
  • This rug's backing and 3/8" wool pile will last longer if you keep it on a rug pad and turn off the beater bar before you vacuum.
  • Follow the care tag instructions and clean all messes with wool detergent to keep your rug soft and beautiful.

Title: Vera Printed - VER01 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
With the ultra-practical Vera collection from Kaleen, it's never been easier to enjoy the look of an antique area rug – even within the most active family homes. The beautiful VER01 area rug draws inspiration from old-world textiles, reimagined with a contemporary twist using smart modern materials for easy everyday care.

  • Vera collection rugs are completely machine washable! Simply launder your rug in your standard home washing machine and enjoy a perfect refresh without booking a single appointment.
  • This bold traditional area rug features a geometric central medallion flanked by intricate detailing throughout an open field, the edges framed in a tidy border. Faux distressed textures lend a vintage look.
  • Pure 100% polyester rug construction makes Vera collection rugs highly resistant against staining and wear. The patterns are printed directly into the fibers. Lightweight construction allows for easy handling.
  • Wash on a cold water cycle using gentle detergent. Do not bleach. Air dry.

Title: Vera Printed - VER05 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Inspired by old-world textiles, the VER05 area rug offers timeless sophistication made to keep up with the busiest modern lifestyles. This exciting interior accent is part of the Vera collection by Kaleen – this series offers classic elegance crafted using the latest technology for family-friendly appeal in every detail.

  • This rug is completely machine washable! Simply run through a standard wash cycle and enjoy a wonderfully refreshed rug, without the need to schedule a cleaning appointment.
  • An oversized center medallion establishes an eye-catching focal point while the layered fields and borders abound with charming intricacy throughout. Use in casual and formal placements alike.
  • Vera VER05 is crafted from resilient polyester rug yarns that resist common types of staining for long-lasting appeal. The slim silhouette and lightweight construction allow for effortless handling.
  • Use a dry white cloth to blot spills upon noticing. Wash in a standard home washing machine using cool water and mild detergent. Air dry. Do not bleach.

Title: Textura - TXT-03 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Displaying a subtle, concentric diamond pattern, our Kaleen Textura TXT-03 area rug offers a touch of visual interest to go with the exceptional comfort of its hand-tufted wool construction..

  • Enjoy a cozy feel underfoot with the Textura collection its hand-tufted wool fibers, which are crafted by talented artisans.
  • Lend a hint of depth and dimension with the understated diamond pattern on this transitional beauty, which easily pairs with traditional or modern settings.
  • These hand-tufted rugs boast medium piles of pure wool, which is crafted by artisans using timeless techniques.
  • Clean regularly by vacuuming on top and beneath, and scrub with a soft brush to help remove stains.

Title: Nomad - NOM-02 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
If you love wool rugs, we think you'll enjoy this beautiful flatwoven NOM-02 area rug from Kaleen's Nomad collection..

  • The Nomad collection from Kaleen features flatweave area rugs that are made using beautiful wool yarns for lasting beauty.
  • This soft wool rug will last longer in a dry room that protects it from excess moisture, which can damage the natural fibers.
  • Keep your rug on a rug pad to protect the 3/8" wool flatweave pile from sliding damage and rotate both the rug and the pad every year.
  • Vacuum without a beater bar to control any shedding that you notice and use a wool detergent when cleaning messes.
Shape (product.metafields.custom.shape): Also in shapes other than rectangle

Title: Brooklyn - Delaney Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Inspired by Persian classics, our Kaleen Brooklyn Delaney area rug has all the charm of a timeless classic along with the must-have comfort of loop-hooked wool, which make it highly versatile, too..

  • Enjoy substantial natural comfort with the loop-hooked wool construction and remarkable strength of the Brooklyn collection.
  • Evoking Persian floor covering of the past, this classic piece boasts sophisticated floral designs that bring a stylish look to any living room, dining room, or bedroom.
  • Our traditional area rug is highlighted by a loop-hooked wool construction and medium pile of yarns.
  • Prolong the life of your rug by thoroughly vacuuming it to remove dirt and debris.

Title: Restoration - RES-04 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Expertly handcrafted by master Kaleen artisans, the Restoration collection seeks to achieve a perfect reproduction of authentic antique rug designs. The handsome RES-04 area rug evokes nostalgia with old-world motifs, its wool surfaces hand-distressed to lend a convincing illusion of age.

  • Choose from three attractive colorways, each one overdyed to produce brilliant depth and dimension.
  • This piece features traditional rug motifs within its open field and stately borders. The surface of each rug is distressed using an innovative hand-shearing technique, each one boasting the worn comfort of a cherished heirloom.
  • Restoration collection area rugs are crafted using time-honored techniques. Each one is hand-knotted from pure 100% wool for dependable longevity. These rugs are completely latex-free. Low-profile construction allows for smooth clearance when placed near doors.
  • Use a dry white cloth to blot spills before they have a chance to set. Always remember to disengage the vacuum beater bar component before vacuuming.
Option1 Value: Dark Chocolate Brown, Milk Chocolate Brown
Color (product.metafields.custom.color): Dark Chocolate Brown, Milk Chocolate Brown (02)

Title: Middleton - MID-01 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Kaleen created the beautiful Middleton collection as an homage to the Duchess of Cambridge herself. The MID-01 area rug boasts a classic bordered design in a range of contemporary colorways..

  • Use this traditional area rug to complement formal and casual spaces alike - the layout is perfect for use beneath dining tables, within social seating spaces, or to center a grand foyer.
  • MID-01 is a 100% wool area rug hand-tufted and hand-finished by skilled Kaleen artisans, then finished with a durable cotton canvas backing
  • Kaleen recommends professional cleaning for all wool area rugs in the Middleton collection. Vacuum regularly with the beater bar disengaged.

Title: Amalie - AML05 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Liven up your patio or play room with the cute, colorful sea life on our Kaleen Amalie AML05 rug. This fun floor covering is crafted of durable synthetic yarns, which allow it to stay inside or go out..

  • Long-lasting polypropylene, which is UV-resistant and soft to the touch, grants this rug incredible versatility and practicality.
  • Vibrant sea creatures pop off the navy field of this coastal accent piece, so you can feature it in any indoor or outdoor setting.
  • Machine-loomed or precision, our resilient synthetic area rug boasts a low profile and can be placed inside or outside.
  • To remove light stains, sponge clean this floor covering with cold water and mild detergent.

Title: PureLife - Winthrop Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Custom rug sizes available. Winding rivers and rugged landscapes serve as the inspiration behind the Winthrop collection, a series of adaptable Kaleen area rugs that transform premium natural materials into impressive works of art sure to elevate any room. This beautiful design features undulating yarns that waver in thickness to create a layered composition with so much nuance to explore.

  • Each area rug in the Winthrop collection is made from premium wool and cotton dyed with freeform-certified dyes. The Global Freeform Textile Standard ensures ethical and sustainable production from start to finish.
  • This natural fiber area rug is available in a curated selection of adaptable neutral colorways. Use as an effective grounding element for cozy retreats and function-forward family spaces alike.
  • Winthrop is pit loomed by skilled artisans using cable flatweave construction, resilient underfoot and simple to maintain. The surface is woven from wool and cotton while the backing is bolstered with jute.
  • Blot away spills using a dry white cloth or a clean sponge. Vacuum in straight lines using a suction-only setting.

Title: Santiago - STG97 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Featuring an abstract look in serene blue tones, our Kaleen Santiago STG97 area rug grants a cool, casual design to any space, indoors or out. Plus, it's crafted of polyester for a soft feel and inherent resilience to foot traffic.

  • In addition to being soft and durable, our Santiago collection is easy to clean and weather-resistant.
  • With a calming blue tone and abstract design, this contemporary floor covering provides a relaxing accent for your patio, sun room, or entryway.
  • Handmade of soft-yet-strong polyester, our indoor/outdoor rug features a low profile so it can easily fit under doors.
  • Avoid excess humidity as this can cause your rug to weaken over time.
  • This rug includes a non-skid backing.
  • Made in India.

Title: Montage - MTG-08 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Make your home even more beautiful when you install this MTG-08 wool area rug from Kaleen's Montage collection..

  • Montage by Kaleen is a collection of transitional area rugs featuring a cut loop wool pile and a modern palette for today's homes.
  • Examine the existing color palette in the room that you're furnishing to help pick the best color variant of this MTG-08 rug for your home.
  • A quality pad placed under this rug will keep it in place, minimizing sliding damage to the backing.
  • Follow the instructions on the care tag to keep this rug clean and in good condition for years to come.

Title: Alzada - ALZ-04 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Immerse yourself in the epitome of contemporary sophistication with the bold Alzada ALZ-04 Area Rug by Kaleen.

  • With its patchwork-style, layered, geometric designs and artistic, natural vibe, this modern area rug is easy to incorporate into any stylish space - yet dramatic enough to stand out among all your one-of-a-kind decor pieces. Choose between a warm, earthy sand, taupe, and gray color palette or a cool blue, denim, and sage colorway for a well-coordinated look.
  • This 100% wool area rug is as stylish as it is versatile. The flat pile area rug is a practical choice for high traffic areas, kid-friendly homes, pet-friendly spaces, and beyond.
  • Brilliant artisans in India have carefully and meticulously hand-tufted this gorgeous area rug.
  • For product longevity, we recommend avoiding the use of a vacuum beater bar on your rug.

Title: Imprints Modern - IPM-01 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Bring beautiful virgin wool into your home when you roll out this IPM-01 area rug from Kaleen's Imprints Modern collection..

  • The Imprints Modern collection from Kaleen features handmade wool area rugs with fashionable contemporary designs.
  • Choose between the color options based on which one fits in with the color palette in the room that you're furnishing.
  • Wool rugs are naturally prone to shedding when they're new, but you can control it without harming the 3/8" pile by vacuuming with the beater bar turned off.
  • Maintain this rug per the instructions from the manufacturer and consider a gentle wool soap to protect the pile.

Title: Origami - ORG-02 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Deliver a zen, artistic look to any room with our Kaleen Origami ORG-02 rug. Hand-tufted of pure wool yarns, this modern floor covering feels extremely soft and is naturally resilient as well..

  • Dense wool yarns are masterfully hand-tufted by artisans, creating a plush surface that acts as a natural insulator.
  • The inviting look of this modern piece comes from its ivory, charcoal, and butterscotch tones as well as the artistic style, so it provides a beautiful foundation for any bedroom, family room, or craft space.
  • Our hand-tufted wool rug features a medium pile height for extra comfort and resilience.
  • Avoid excess humidity as this can cause your rug to weaken over time.

Title: Broadloom - Necker Island Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Custom rug sizes available. Energize your favorite interior spaces with the Necker Island area rug, a striking Kaleen design made with an eye-catching geometric pattern that covers the surface. This attractive area rug is handcrafted from premium wool for long-lasting performance even within active placements.

  • Necker Island area rugs are child-friendly and pet-friendly. The flatwoven surface allows for easy cleanup while standing strong against everyday wear.
  • Concentric diamond patterns decorate this geometric area rug using a simple two-tone format. Choose from a variety of colorways ranging from simple neutrals to bright eye-catching hues.
  • Kaleen weavers craft every Necker Island rug using traditional looms for true artisanal appeal. The surface is woven from 100% wool for underfoot comfort while the backing is stabilized with strong cotton canvas.
  • Use a dry white cloth to blot spills before they set. Always remember to disengage the vacuum beater bar component before vacuuming.

Title: Broadloom - Vail Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Custom rug sizes available. The attractive Vail area rug draws inspiration from the enchanting landscape of the famous ski town that shares its name – its colors are natural and its textures are rugged yet wonderfully soft to the touch. This go-anywhere Kaleen design is handcrafted from premium materials for truly adaptable appeal.

  • Vail is a fantastic area rug for homes with pets and children. The wool pile is comfortable underfoot yet stands up beautifully to higher levels of foot traffic.
  • This simple solid area rug design enjoys subtle tonality for an elevated decorative aesthetic. The looped pile is randomly sheared in places, creating a subtle cascade of light and shadow that washes across the surface.
  • Each rug in the Vail collection is hand loomed by skilled Kaleen artisans with a 100% wool rug surface that is backed with sturdy cotton canvas. Custom sizing makes this collection perfect for spaces with uncommon proportions.
  • Use a dry white cloth to blot spills immediately upon noticing. Vacuum in straight lines using a suction-only setting or hard surface attachment.

Title: Tara Rounds - Pablo - 7703 Area Rug

Show off your style in any space with this Pablo - 7703 area rug design from the Tara Rounds collection.

  • The Tara Rounds collection features handmade wool area rugs with a timeless palette for today's homes.

Title: Elijah - ELI95 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Botanical motifs flourish on our Kaleen Elijah ELI95 rug, creating a fresh-yet-classic look that adds elegance to any space. Even better, this piece is hand-tufted of thick wool, so it feels great underfoot.

  • Wool is naturally soft and resilient, making this hand-tufted collection a favorite of those who want the best of both worlds.
  • Featuring an intricate, traditional design in an irregular pattern, this traditional beauty brings chic sophistication to your dining room, bedroom, or office.
  • Our hand-tufted area rug is crafted of 100% wool in a medium pile of yarns for must-feel softness.
  • Embedded dirt and debris are most easily removed by routinely vacuuming your rug.
  • Made in India.

  • Wool is naturally soft and resilient, making this hand-tufted collection a favorite of those who want the best of both worlds.
  • Featuring an intricate, traditional design in an irregular pattern, this traditional beauty brings chic sophistication to your dining room, bedroom, or office.
  • Our hand-tufted area rug is crafted of 100% wool in a medium pile of yarns for must-feel softness.
  • Embedded dirt and debris are most easily removed by routinely vacuuming your rug.
  • Made in India.

Title: Elijah - ELI99 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Ornate designs have never been more approachable than on our Kaleen Elijah ELI99 rug thanks to hand-dyed, high-contrast tones. This hand-tufted wool beauty is also a treat for bare feet.

  • Skillfully hand-tufted of wool by artisans using time-honored methods, this piece boasts craftsmanship and comfort underfoot.
  • By giving this floor covering high-contrast colors, we refreshed its traditional look, making it an elegant-yet-casual option for your living room, guest bedroom, or entryway.
  • Our hand-tufted, hand-dyed wool rug features a medium pile height for remarkable softness.
  • The easiest form of rug maintenance is consistent vacuuming, which will prolong the life of your rug.
  • Made in India.

Title: Regency Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Create the perfect color statement for your space with the highly versatile Regency area rug collection from Kaleen. This collection features simple bordered designs that look great anywhere, available in a diverse variety of colorways to flatter any interior decor theme – the options are endless.

  • Regency is a collection made with active family homes in mind. These rugs are made from premium wool for enduring strength, ideal for hardwearing interior placements like living rooms and dining rooms.
  • Select from a wide variety of colors. This contemporary area rug features a two-tone design, with the thick border a little darker than the open field. Abrash coloration lends rich tonal dimension to the surface.
  • Kaleen weavers loom every Regency area rug by hand for artisanal appeal. This 100% wool area rug features a low-cropped pile for easier everyday maintenance, perfect for busy modern lifestyles.
  • Use a dry white cloth to blot spills before they set. Some shedding is to be expected. This will lessen over time with regular vacuuming.

  • Select from a wide variety of colors. This contemporary area rug features a two-tone design, with the thick border a little darker than the open field. Abrash coloration lends rich tonal dimension to the surface.
  • Kaleen weavers loom every Regency area rug by hand for artisanal appeal. This 100% wool area rug features a low-cropped pile for easier everyday maintenance, perfect for busy modern lifestyles.
  • Use a dry white cloth to blot spills before they set. Some shedding is to be expected. This will lessen over time with regular vacuuming.

Title: Origami - ORG-01 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Reminiscent of ornate, Art Deco designs, the Kaleen Origami ORG-01 area rug offers a dramatic look that's beautifully hand-tufted of 100% wool by artisans, resulting in an ultra-soft statement piece..

  • Each of these super soft wool floor coverings is meticulously hand-tufted by artisans using time-tested methods.
  • The geometric design of this chic piece is inspired by the ancient art of Japanese paper folding, which delivers it a striking look that's perfect for any living room, bedroom, or entryway.
  • A medium pile of wool makes our hand-tufted rug incredibly soft and surprisingly strong.
  • Do not place your rug in direct sunlight because this will make it fade over time.

Title: Renaissance - Hand Loomed Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Redecorate your space with this unique Hand Loomed Renaissance rug from Kaleen. This monochromatic collection features a traditional soft backing with a soft virgin wool pile for years of elegant durability.

  • This Hand Loomed Renaissance rug is handmade in India with a 1/4" 100% virgin seasonal wool pile and a sturdy-yet-soft backing.
  • The Hand Loomed Renaissance is available in multiple colors, including butterscotch, blue, graphite, salsa, aubergine, cardinal, emerald, chocolate, silver, copper, pink, ivory, turquoise, and brown.
  • We recommend keeping your Hand Loomed Renaissance rug on a quality pad to protect the soft backing and 1/4" wool pile from surface damage.
  • Follow the care tag instructions when cleaning your rug and blot all spills immediately with a soft, dry sponge.

Redecorate your space with this unique Hand Loomed Renaissance rug from Kaleen. This monochromatic collection features a traditional soft backing with a soft virgin wool pile for years of elegant durability.

  • This Hand Loomed Renaissance rug is handmade in India with a 1/4" 100% virgin seasonal wool pile and a sturdy-yet-soft backing.
  • The Hand Loomed Renaissance is available in multiple colors, including butterscotch, blue, graphite, salsa, aubergine, cardinal, emerald, chocolate, silver, copper, pink, ivory, turquoise, and brown.
  • We recommend keeping your Hand Loomed Renaissance rug on a quality pad to protect the soft backing and 1/4" wool pile from surface damage.
  • Follow the care tag instructions when cleaning your rug and blot all spills immediately with a soft, dry sponge.

Redecorate your space with this unique Hand Loomed Renaissance rug from Kaleen. This monochromatic collection features a traditional soft backing with a soft virgin wool pile for years of elegant durability.

  • This Hand Loomed Renaissance rug is handmade in India with a 1/4" 100% virgin seasonal wool pile and a sturdy-yet-soft backing.
  • The Hand Loomed Renaissance is available in multiple colors, including butterscotch, blue, graphite, salsa, aubergine, cardinal, emerald, chocolate, silver, copper, pink, ivory, turquoise, and brown.
  • We recommend keeping your Hand Loomed Renaissance rug on a quality pad to protect the soft backing and 1/4" wool pile from surface damage.
  • Follow the care tag instructions when cleaning your rug and blot all spills immediately with a soft, dry sponge.

Title: Broadloom - Eustatia Island Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Custom rug sizes available. Let the fashion forward Eustatia Island area rug bring understated sophistication to any of your favorite placements throughout the home. This attractive area rug is handwoven by the skilled artisans at Kaleen, its surface imbued with a bold chevron herringbone pattern reminiscent of high-end apparel – timeless and easy to coordinate.

  • Eustatia Island is inspired by luxury textiles, perfect for the most well-curated interior spaces. These rugs are most suitable for living spaces, offices, bedrooms, and more.
  • Choose from a variety of adaptable neutral-leaning colorways that vary by intensity. Some of these contemporary rugs enjoy lower contrast for a subtle look while others go bold for an eye-catching effect.
  • Each rug in the Eustatia Island collection treats the senses by combining the comfort of wool with the glamorous sheen of viscose. These rugs are handwoven by skilled artisans, the blended face backed with cotton canvas for strength.
  • Avoid prolonged contact with moisture by blotting spills immediately using a dry white cloth or a clean sponge. Vacuum using a suction-only setting.

Title: Lauderdale - LDD-01 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Enjoy cozy go-anywhere comfort with the wonderfully adaptable Lauderdale LDD-01 area rug by Kaleen. This delightful design is crafted from smart modern synthetics for use indoors and outdoors alike, made strong to resist the elements for long-lasting style in every environment.

  • Lauderdale collection area rugs are crafted with UV-resistant materials to withstand fading even in the sunlight, resistant against water for excellent performance in the rain or at the poolside.
  • Use this contemporary area rug in hardwearing indoor placements like dining rooms and entryways or let its weather resistance shine in a patio setting. Choose from a range of versatile color options to suit any theme.
  • This indoor/outdoor synthetic rug is crafted from 100% PET polyester, hand-loomed by skilled Kaleen artisans. Non-skid backing ensures secure placement.
  • Always disengage the vacuum beater bar component before vacuuming. Spot clean using mild soap and cool water.

Title: Minkah - MKH-03 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Add subtle elegance to any indoor or outdoor area with this MKH-03 area rug design from the Minkah collection.

  • The Minkah collection features beautiful indoor/outdoor area rugs with a handmade carved pile for eye-catching designs.
  • This rug's hand-loomed polyester pile is UV-treated so that it can stand up to any setting without worry-place it indoors or outdoors for lasting floor protection.
  • Rotate your rug every year and rely on the K-Stop non-skid backing to prevent sliding damage to the 1/4" polyester pile.
  • Clean your rug regularly and vacuum it without a beater bar to keep it in excellent condition for as long as possible.

Title: Montage - MTG-09 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Give your home some chic vibes when you install this vintage wool MTG-09 area rug from Kaleen's Montage collection..

  • The Montage collection features wool area rugs from Kaleen with transitional designs that draw inspiration from a diverse range of cultures.
  • Choose the color variant of this rug that will look best with the existing decor you have in your home.

Title: Radiance - RAD97 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Our Kaleen Radiance RAD97 area rug is masterfully hand-tufted of wool by artisans and balances restful green tones with a chic contemporary look. In other words, it's a soft, stylish foundation piece.

  • The hand-tufted wool construction of our Radiance collection grants natural comfort underfoot without sacrificing durability.
  • Relaxing shades of green and a metallic printed foil base give our contemporary floor covering a luxe look that easily complements traditional, global, or boho chic styles.
  • Our medium-pile wool area rug is meticulously hand-tufted by artisans using time-honored techniques.
  • Rotate your rug every couple of months to alleviate repeated wear and tear only on certain areas.
  • Made in India.

Title: Radiance - RAD99 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Metallic accents on hand-tufted wool give our Kaleen Radiance RAD99 rug a chic appearance and soft feel. Plus, the design is actually carved by artisans for a unique texture and look.

  • Comfort and durability are apparent on our Radiance collection thanks to its hand-tufted wool construction and cotton backing.
  • With a contemporary design featuring a silver printed foil base, this beautiful blue floor covering creates a casual-yet-luxe look for your living room, bedroom, or entryway.
  • A medium pile of wool yarns is hand-tufted by artisans and back by a signature cotton canvas, giving this soft indoor rug a touch of resilience.
  • Consistent vacuuming is the best and easiest way to keep rug fibers strong and healthy.
  • Made in India.

Title: Luminary - LUM-01 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Anchor your space in a soft and simple way with the gorgeous Luminary LUM-01 Area Rug by Kaleen.

  • This contemporary rug offers hand-loomed construction and a texture that's as easy on the eyes as it is on the feet.
  • Available in a wide array of breathtaking hues, this charming, low pile rug is a perfectly effortless addition to just about any space in your well-edited home.
  • The soft and supple viscose and wool area rug promises a soft feel and a luxe, high-quality look - complete with a subtle sheen.
  • For product longevity, we recommend avoiding the use of a vacuum beater bar on your rug.

Title: Broadloom - Peter Island Stripe Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Custom rug sizes available. Slender pinstripes sweep across the surface of the Peter Island Stripe area rug, a sophisticated Kaleen design that draws inspiration from luxury apparel fabrics – sure to lend a fashionable element to any space. This beautiful design is handcrafted from natural wool for quality you can see and feel in every detail.

  • This area rug is flatwoven for excellent performance in demanding spaces like dining rooms, home offices, living space, and more. The smooth surface is ideal for standalone placement and layering alike.
  • Peter Island Stripe features a tasteful chevron pattern rendered in tonal neutrals while contrasting pinstripes sweep from one end to the other. Use this light striped area rug as an uplifting element for your favorite spaces.
  • Highly skilled Kaleen artisans weave every Peter Island area rug by hand. The 100% wool surface is beautifully flatwoven with exceptional density for strength while sturdy cotton canvas bolsters the backing.
  • Use a dry white cloth to blot spills. Vacuum using a suction-only setting. Rotate twice per year and invest in professional cleaning as needed.

Title: Broadloom - Peter Island Stripe Area Rug
Marble - MBL-01 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
If you love natural textures and themes, we think you'll fall for this MBL-01 area rug from Kaleen's Marble collection..

  • The Marble collection from Kaleen features beautiful hand-tufted wool area rugs with marbled designs that'll make you do a doubletake.
  • Wool is a natural fiber that lasts longer when it's kept away from moisture and soil, so choose a dry area that's protected from heavy shoe traffic.
  • Vacuuming with the beater bar turned off will help you maintain your wool rug and control shedding, which is natural when the rug is new.
  • Use a quality pad underneath your rug and a gentle wool soap to clean messes so that the 3/8" wool pile is protected for years to come.

Title: Brushstrokes - BRS-02 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Super bold color combinations make the BRS-02 area rug a stunning statement piece for any room. This accent is part of the Brushstrokes collection by Kaleen, a series of artful watercolor-like creations rendered in plush 100% wool..

  • Kaleen artisans use a unique primitive dyeing technique to bring rich tonal variation to every yarn.
  • An expressive large-scale ogee trellis bounds from edge to edge over a creative field. Use this contemporary area rug beneath a dining table, within a casual seating area, or even in the home office.
  • Each wool area rug in the Brushstrokes collection is tufted and finished by hand, the soft cut pile backed with a strong cotton canvas for lasting durability.
  • Vacuum using a suction-only setting. Invest in professional cleaning periodically.

  • Kaleen artisans use a unique primitive dyeing technique to bring rich tonal variation to every yarn.
  • An expressive large-scale ogee trellis bounds from edge to edge over a creative field. Use this contemporary area rug beneath a dining table, within a casual seating area, or even in the home office.
  • Each wool area rug in the Brushstrokes collection is tufted and finished by hand, the soft cut pile backed with a strong cotton canvas for lasting durability.
  • Vacuum using a suction-only setting. Invest in professional cleaning periodically.

Title: Calvin - CLV99 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Incredibly versatile, our Kaleen Calvin CLV99 rug offers a chic look that freshens up any space, but its hand-tufted construction of 100% wool is sure to steal the show with its remarkably soft feel.

  • Tufted, carved, and surged by hand, this piece is rich in texture, resilience, and craftsmanship.
  • The casual, transitional style of this piece lends it incredible versatility, so it can easily harmonize with traditional, contemporary, and global looks.
  • With a plush pile of hand-spun wool yarns, this hand-tufted area rug provides exceptional comfort and natural durability.
  • To clean area rugs, vacuum regularly and quickly blot spills as soon as they occur.
  • Made in India.

Title: Alejandra - ALJ97 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Enjoy the geometric and Southwestern accents on our Kaleen Alejandra ALJ97 rug wherever you need an infusion of energy and style. This gorgeous piece is hand-woven of natural fibers for incredible softness underfoot.

  • Skillfully hand-woven of jute and wool, this natural beauty delivers comfort and an easy-to-clean quality.
  • Inspired by classic Southwestern designs, our cozy floor covering adds warmth and comfort to your living room, man cave, or bedroom.
  • This jute and wool rug features a high pile of masterfully hand-woven fibers and elephant-style tassels for extra texture.
  • By routinely vacuuming your rug, you will prolong its life and maintain the strength of its fibers.
  • Made in India.

Title: PureLife - Weatherby Cove Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Custom rug sizes available. Textural stripes bring added dimension to the Weatherby Cove area rug, a beautifully handwoven design made by the master artisans at Kaleen. Each rug is constructed from premium quality materials made to keep up with all the demands of a vibrant family home.

  • Feel confident using your Weatherby Cove area rug in homes with pets and children. These rugs are made from pure wool and freeform-certified dyes for safety, comfort, and resilience.
  • Cut and loop pile construction carves attractive stripes across the surface of this simple solid rug collection. Select from a variety of neutral colorways sure to flatter any interior palette.
  • Kaleen artisans loom every Weatherby Cove area rug by hand. The 100% wool rug face is adorned with thick loops and plush cut pile, the backing bolstered by jute and cotton for strength.
  • Professional cleaning is recommended. Use a dry white cloth to blot spills before they set. Always remember to disengage the vacuum beater bar component before vacuuming.

Title: PureLife - Martinique Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Custom rug sizes available. Premium materials meet fashion-forward construction with the highly innovative Martinique area rug collection from Kaleen. These quality handwoven area rugs are handmade by master artisans using pure wool for comfort and dependable resilience.

  • Feel encouraged to use this area rug in any of your most demanding settings. The flatwoven wool construction is resilient against wear for dependable performance in dining rooms, playrooms, living rooms, and more.
  • Martinique is a chic contemporary area rug decorated with a stylish pinstripe pattern, with a dense chevron weave alternating between sections. Choose from a curated selection of neutral-based colorways for easy coordination.
  • Highly skilled Kaleen artisans weave every Martinique rug by hand using all-natural wool dyed using certified-freeform dyes. The backing is bolstered with jute and cotton canvas.
  • Professional cleaning is recommended as needed. Vacuum using a suction-only setting and blot spills using a dry white cloth or a clean sponge.

Title: PureLife - Martinique Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Custom rug sizes available. Premium materials meet fashion-forward construction with the highly innovative Martinique area rug collection from Kaleen. These quality handwoven area rugs are handmade by master artisans using pure wool for comfort and dependable resilience.

  • Feel encouraged to use this area rug in any of your most demanding settings. The flatwoven wool construction is resilient against wear for dependable performance in dining rooms, playrooms, living rooms, and more.
  • Martinique is a chic contemporary area rug decorated with a stylish pinstripe pattern, with a dense chevron weave alternating between sections. Choose from a curated selection of neutral-based colorways for easy coordination.
  • Highly skilled Kaleen artisans weave every Martinique rug by hand using all-natural wool dyed using certified-freeform dyes. The backing is bolstered with jute and cotton canvas.
  • Professional cleaning is recommended as needed. Vacuum using a suction-only setting and blot spills using a dry white cloth or a clean sponge.

Title: Global Inspirations - GLB-12 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Fans of transitional decor will enjoy this beautiful GLB-12 area rug from the Global Inspirations collection from Kaleen.

  • Global Inspirations by Kaleen is a line of high-quality handmade wool rugs imported from India, and each one features a design inspired by cultures around the world.
  • Choose the color option that will look best with your room's existing interior color story for the best results.
  • This rug is hand-tufted in India using pure wool dyed with traditional methods for colors that pop, and it is fixed on a cotton canvas backing for durability.
  • Clean your rug regularly according to the manufacturer's instructions and control natural wool shedding by vacuuming without a beater bar.

Title: Amalie - AML08 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Simply yet stylish, the beautiful border design on our Kaleen Amalie AML08 rug helps perfectly frame any space, from your patio to your living room. Even better, this piece is crafted of durable synthetic yarns for long-lasting comfort underfoot..

  • Naturally UV-resistant and easy to maintain courtesy of its synthetic construction, the Amalie collection is perfect for patios or high-traffic spaces.
  • A gorgeous border and simple design lend incredible versatility to this floor covering, so you can feature it in dining or entertaining spaces, inside or out.
  • For precision, this stylish rug is power-loomed into a low pile height of resilient polypropylene.
  • Regular vacuuming extends the longevity of your rug by removing embedded dirt and debris.

Title: Alzada - ALZ-02 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Elevate your interior with the contemporary treasure that is the breathtaking Alzada ALZ-02 Area Rug by Kaleen.

  • Featuring a neutral palette of earthy sand, taupe, and gray tones, an abstract, geometric, patchwork-style pattern, and plenty of effortless style and sophistication, this modern area rug is the perfect way to add character and depth to your everyday life.
  • Ideal for spaces with heavy foot traffic, pet- and kid-friendly homes, and more, this flat pile area rug delivers both practicality and style. The 100% wool area rug is effortlessly versatile and undeniably lovely.
  • This versatile, yet completely unique area rug is hand-tufted in India.
  • To keep your gorgeous rug looking fresh between professional cleanings, spot cleaning with a white cloth is recommended.

Title: Mercery - MER-01 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
The exciting Mercery collection draws inspiration from traditional Tibetan textiles, each piece featuring expressive patterns reimagined in contemporary colorways for flexible decorative possibilities. The handsome MER-01 area rug features premium handcrafted construction made by the skilled artisans at Kaleen.

  • Select from two colorways – one bold, and one neutral. Each one features subtle tonal variation for endless coordination possibilities.
  • Mercery MER-01 features expressive flourishes that decorate the surface from edge to edge unbound by border. The lines waver and wander to underscore the handcrafted provenance of each rug.
  • This hand-tufted area rug collection is made using a combination of resilient wool and silky soft viscose. Use this blended rug in comfort-centric placements like bedrooms, living rooms, offices, and more.
  • Avoid prolonged contact with moisture. Blot spills immediately using a dry white cloth or a clean sponge.

Title: Broadloom - Boca Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Custom rug sizes available. Create spaces that perfectly reflect your own unique style – indoors or outdoors – with the wonderfully flexible Boca area rug collection by Kaleen. Each area rug is made with resilient weather-resistant materials that can keep up with all your most demanding placements.

  • Smart synthetic fibers give Boca rugs the softness to satisfy while providing excellent resistance against moisture, staining, fading, and foot traffic. Use in hardwearing indoor placements like dining rooms or cozy outdoor hangouts like patios and balconies.
  • Boca is available in a variety of colorways ranging from brilliant jewel tones to adaptable go-anywhere neutrals. Each one enjoys rich patterning created using thick yarns in bold contrasting colors, lending an almost geometric quality to the surface.
  • Although Boca collection rugs are durable enough for the outdoors, they're crafted with the same care and artistry as the most luxurious indoor rugs. Each one is hand loomed by skilled artisans with a 100% PET polyester rug surface and a reinforced backing.
  • To clean, spritz soiled areas with a solution of diluted dish soap and cool water. Rinse with a garden hose and allow to dry.

Add elegant Moroccan designs with this soft wool CAS-02 area rug design from Kaleen's Casablanca collection..

Title: PureLife - Longwood Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Custom rug sizes available. Set a sophisticated tone wherever you spend your time with the Longwood area rug by the skilled artisans at Kaleen. This handsome accent showcases the best of handcrafted construction, made from premium materials that will provide dependable comfort and style for years of enjoyment.

  • Choose from a variety of neutral colorways to suit a wide variety of decor themes, each one dyed using quality freeform-certified dyes to ensure safety and sustainability throughout the collection.
  • Longwood is a contemporary area rug that keeps things simple with a solid base, interwoven with dark and light strands that trace a dynamic linear pattern across the surface.
  • Kaleen artisans weave every Longwood area rug by hand, tailored to any size that you request. These 100% wool rugs feature a cut and loop pile imbued with exquisite tonal dimension.
  • Use a dry white cloth to blot spills. Vacuum in straight lines using a suction-only setting. Invest in professional cleaning as needed.

Title: PureLife - Springfield Corner Area Rug

Make any room in your home feel more modern and intentional with this CAS-03 area rug design from Kaleen's Casablanca collection..

  • The Casablanca collection from Kaleen features stunning hand-tufted wool area rugs with natural colors and Moroccan designs.
  • Choose between the color variants of this area rug based on how each one would look in the room that you're furnishing.
  • We recommend vacuuming without a beater bar to control any wool shedding that you notice-turning off the beater bar protects the 3/8" wool pile.
  • Clean this rug with a wool-specific detergent according to the instructions on the care tag to keep it beautiful for years to come.

Title: Effete - EFE96 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Bursting with global charm, our Kaleen Effete EFE96 rug features a classic appearance that easily blends with traditional or contemporary styles. Plus, it's hand-tufted of wool, so it's remarkably soft underfoot.

  • Masterfully hand-tufted by artisans using time-honored techniques, this collection is a comfortable work of craftsmanship.
  • Detailed designs inspired by timeless architecture give this gray-hued, transitional piece an elegant-yet-inviting look that is well suited for living rooms, bedrooms, and offices.
  • Tufted by hand from blended wool, this transitional rug boasts a soft, medium pile height.
  • Gently brush area rugs with a carpet brush or sweeper to remove pet hairs and other stubborn debris.
  • Made in India.

Title: Effete - EFE97 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Deliver sophisticated global charm to any living or dining space with our Kaleen Effete EFE97 area rug, which is hand-tufted entirely of wool by artisans for exceptional comfort and a touch of durability.

  • Naturally soft and durable, our Effete collection is hand-tufted by artisans for outstanding craftsmanship as well.
  • Evoking classic architecture, this navy, transitional piece lends casual elegance to your living room, office, or bedroom.
  • With a medium pile of wool yarns, this hand-tufted area rug offers plenty of comfort and durability.
  • Stubborn pet hairs are most easily removed by gently using a carpet brush or carpet sweeper.
  • Made in India.

Title: Effete - EFE99 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
Inspired by ancient Roman and Greek architecture, our Kaleen Effete EFE99 rug combines classic style with a comfy, hand-tufted wool construction resulting in an extremely versatile piece.

  • Hand-tufted of 100% wool by artisans, our Effete collection offers natural softness and insulation.
  • Whether you're placing this floor covering in a global study or contemporary living room, it easily complements the space thanks to its transitional style and inviting ivory tone.
  • Featuring a blended wool construction, this hand-tufted area rug has a medium pile of yarns for incredible comfort.
  • Brushing your rug is the easiest way to get rid of unwanted pet hairs that have become embedded in the fibers.
  • Made in India.

Title: Solitaire - SOL-09 Area Rug
Body (HTML):
The luxurious texture and sheen of our Kaleen Solitaire SOL-09 rug comes from its handwoven viscose makeup, while its simple-yet-stylish, Southwestern design offers instant visual interest to any room in your home..

  • Each rug in the Solitaire collection is meticulously handwoven of silky, shiny viscose by artisans for a luxe look and feel.
  • Inspired by upscale Tibetan rugs, this Southwestern beauty lends simple beauty to your study, living room, or master suite thanks to its tribal-influenced design.
  • Our handwoven viscose rugs boast a low profile for even more comfort underfoot.
  • Clean your area rug regularly by vacuuming it on top and beneath every once in a while.
